<div dir="ltr"><div>Hi Eugene,<br></div><div>carto file is a file with a staic graph topology of your node.</div><div>in the opal/mca/carto/file/carto_file.h you can see example.</div><div>( yes I know that , it should be help/man list :) )</div>
<div>Basically it describes a map of your node and inside interconnection.</div><div></div><div>Hopefully it will be discovered automatically someday, </div><div>but for now you can describe your node manually.</div><div>
